title: Peter Joback - Det har ar platsen 2004
description:
Maybe one of my most important albums.
A very exciting recording and writing period preceded this album. Mauro Scocco wrote me songs after the two of us having long discussions about life. So did Niclas Frisk and Andreas Mattson.
